[SN]TITLE[SN]
Falkirk 3-2 St Mirren

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Falkirk got the better of St Mirren to go six points clear of third-placed Hibernian in the Scottish Championship.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
