Lee Miller nodded a Myles Hippolyte cross beyond Jamie Langfield to put the Bairns ahead but Stephen Mallan's free-kick levelled matters.
Bob McHugh headed the Bairns back ahead but Mallan equalised a second time, firing past Danny Rogers.
But Blair Alston struck in the last minute to secure victory for Peter Houston's side.
